      Can you upload PNG to Facebook?
      3. Facebook post image size.

      You can upload files in any of the following formats: JPEG, BMP, PNG, GIF, or TIFF. If you're uploading a PNG file, it's best to keep the file size below 1MB. PNG files larger than 1MB may appear pixelated.

      How do I add a logo to my Facebook profile picture?
      To add or change your profile picture:
      1. Sign in to Facebook and go to your Page.
      2. Hover over your profile picture and click the camera icon.
      3. Select Upload Photo.
      4. Choose your logo file and click Open. Crop and position as needed.
      5. Click Save.
